            "answer_text": "NIOS Exam is Hard! For those who haven\u2019t studied. NIOS Exam is Easy! For those who have given time and effort in their study. Simply it depends upon your preparation. If ones preparation has been in disciplined manner, studying the standard textbooks and revising it, practice of solved question papers, and supported by NIOS guide books and help books. Then, the NIOS Exam is an easy walk. And for those, who didn\u2019t followed any of the above action, NIOS exam is very hard to crack. Students must take it, simply as an exam - neither hard nor easy. They must focus in their preparation. That\u2019s all. ",
